Windows
* pre Windows 2000 support


Pre Windows 2000 support
If you need pre Windows 2000 support make sure WINVER is defined correctly
libbfio uses WINVER to determine the available WINAPI functions


MacOS X
* missing libtoolize
* building multiple architure binaries


Missing libtoolize
Use glibtoolize instead


Building multiple architecture binaries
I.e. on MacOS X 10.4 run the following commands:
CFLAGS="-isysroot /Developer/SDKs/MacOSX10.4u.sdk -arch ppc -arch i386" \
LDFLAGS="-Wl,-syslibroot,/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX10.4u.sdk -arch ppc -arch i386" \
./configure --disable-dependency-tracking --prefix=$PWD/macosx/tmp/
make
make install

The binaries are installed in $PWD/macosx/tmp/

